<br>
I was just posting to ask if anyone has noticed anything different about Vox recently. My guild alliance on Karana just tried to take her down last night with 7 very good groups, and we were owned. We were all Dragon vets as well. We had cleared her lair, and after buff line and such, we charged, only to see things pop, not agro from somewhere else, but pop the second we attacked Vox. It seems they were not on the 2 hour timer anymore, as we were in her lair 1 1/2 hours after it was cleared. We tried 2 times, had 5 adds both times, which was simply too many to try and deal with. I also heard reports of her being more resistent then usual, not to mention healing at 50% (though that was prolly the IG priest that poped in the lair). Anyway, just curious if anyone had noticed similar things on other servers, and if so, how they dealt with it. <p><p ALIGN=CENTER>
